## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and publications. Some sources may not reflect the most current trends or changes in educational policies. Additionally, the focus was primarily on U.S. public schools, which may not fully represent the global context of social class and education. Further research could explore longitudinal studies and international comparisons to provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.

